description: This version of the  Index Pointing Up emoji has the  Medium-dark Skin Tone applied, which is displayed as a Dark Brown Skin Tone on sup
apple_vendor_description: The index pointing up emoji with a medium-dark skin tone on Apple devices is depicted with a strong, defined finger with a soft, rounded tip, pointing directly upwards. Apple's signature glossy shading and realistic lighting give it a polished, authoritative presence, emphasizing direction or emphasis. This emoji is commonly used on Apple devices to highlight a point, indicate a suggestion, or signify the number one.
